   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
    "Print", "[", "\"\<Thus, we immediately get the standard Case b initial \
set of equations, and they are \
\!\(\*StyleBox[\"identical\",FontSlant->\"Italic\"]\) to the Case 4D_b \
