Cell[BoxData["\<\"Normally we restrict this case to B(t,r)=\[CapitalBeta](r) \
and \[DoubleStruckCapitalC](t,r)=\[GothicCapitalC](r). But, in this instance \
we start with more general B(t,r) and show right away that, in fact, we get \
B(t,r)=\[CapitalBeta](r).\"\>"], "Print",
