Cell[BoxData["\<\"In order for \[CapitalBeta] to be a strict function of r, \
the \\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(\[PartialD]\\), \\(r\\)]\\)A(t,r) term in the \
numerator must be proportional to A(t,r). This is so that the numerator A \
